parameters: There's a strong-looking monster.... Will you fight it?

It's a monument to commemorate the defeat of a unique
monster.... \! Lizard Knight, would you like to have a
rematch? \!

That person is Mr. Magnus. He helped us with various things.
Setting up character illustrations, arranging monsters...
adjusting boss stats... It's really amazing, isn't it?

He's mysteriously motivated and tells us all about his days
off. He's working really hard, so I want you to give him
words of encouragement. Look, it's time to leave a
comment...!!

Welcome, dechi! Since I'm a capitalist, I'll explain without
hesitation, dechi!! What would you like to know about the
participation project, dechi?
What kind of atmosphere is planned?

We're planning to create a VIP Map that you can visit in the
game, dechi! Whether it will be a Café, a Casino, or a Maid
Café...! We haven't decided yet, dechi!

Everyone, please become an NPC over there! DL games will
become a permanent form, you know! Leave a mark and a proof
of life in modern society! I wonder how well it will sell.

It's not really that expensive, dechi! Just endure not doing
a 5-pull gacha or something, dechi! Let's become an
exhibition together...!! Dechi!!

Of course, you can choose, dechi! Since it's complicated,
I'll explain them one by one, dechi!
If you want to make it yourself

Give me a rough idea of the atmosphere, and I'll create it
over here! Gender, clothing, color... Around that area,
dechi! Animals or monsters are also okay, dechi! In that
case, the atmosphere will be limited, though, dechi...

On the one hand, it's the easiest option, but there may be
cases where it doesn't match your image... Since a retake is
probably not possible, it's more suitable for people who
don't mind not being too particular about their appearance,
dechi.
Is there anything else you want to ask, dechi!?

There's a god who distributes copyright-free walking
materials, dechi. If you search for RPG Maker and walking
materials, you'll find plenty, dechi. Find the ideal body to
put your soul into, dechi!

The recommended specifications are MZ or MV, dechi! Using
any other specifications may result in blurry images, so I
don't recommend it, dechi! If the main and material overlap,
I'd like to consult with you, dechi!

Each one has its own Terms of Service to be aware of, dechi!
It may be prohibited for questionable individuals, so in
that case, it's not possible, dechi! If possible, it's also
best to avoid using copyrighted materials, dechi!
Is there anything else you want to ask, dechi!?

It's okay if you can draw, you can draw it yourself, dechi!
Even if you can't draw pixels, there are ways to create it
yourself, dechi! It's become a convenient era, dechi!!

You can use the 30-day free trial version of RPG Maker MV
and RPG Maker MZ, dechi! With this, even if you can't draw,
you can easily create pixel characters, dechi!

The issues are that you need to have a computer! The
software's usage is a bit troublesome! There's a 30-day
limit!... Around that area, dechi.

It may take a little extra effort, but you can become the
appearance you desire, dechi. Oh, by the way, if you want to
become a child, please use MZ, dechi.
Is there anything else you want to ask, dechi!?

Of course, you can speak however you like, dechi! You can
choose your own name and lines, dechi!

Don't think too hard, dechi! Take my chatter as an example,
dechi! Learn by watching the back of your senpai, dechi!

However, discrimination and slander... all of that is
absolutely not allowed, dechi! Even vertical reading is
absolutely not allowed, dechi! Compliance is important,
dechi! But, it's okay to have adult content, dechi. It's
okay to sexually harass the characters, dechi.

It's impossible if it's too long, dechi. I want to summarize
it in about two windows, dechi. Please help me with your
cooperation, dechi.

There may be revisions and proofreading due to
circumstances. Please also understand that point.

Ah, on the contrary, it's also fine to have spirits without
names or lines, dechi. It's easier that way, dechi. For both
of us. However, there are technical issues, so really
difficult ones are impossible, dechi!

I've put a link in the summary section, dechi! Please check
there for further details! Dechi!

Imagine this place being expanded, dechi! It depends on the
number of people, dechi...!! I can't read this part either,
dechi! We'll do some image training because there are a few
people, dechi!!
Well then, see you later! Dechi!!

I will explain the detailed abilities of each character and
recommend the best way to fight.

The selling point is the flexibility to change movements
according to the situation! Let's fight in various ways like
a true protagonist!

The recommended approach is to use the Radiant Sword to
maintain attack power, and if necessary, provide support
including items! For characters with low SP, use the
Cheerful Aile!

You can use the Secret Technique without consuming any
turns! Don't let it go to waste, so let's use it wisely!
With the \i[97] Kasumi Sandan, you can also recover SP!

Depending on her approach, she can even pull off some
outrageous fighting styles...!
\}Please let me know if something is really broken.

The Secret Technique that increases the number of actions is
super strong. \! Keep it in mind for now. \. Let's try using
it! \! You'll also gain more magic that you can use!

Should we debuff the enemy, focus on healing, or go on the
offensive...? Let's make the most of our limited 4 turns!
\}Hmm, did I make it too strong...?

As a tank, she can reduce the damage taken! \! We can weaken
the enemy, strengthen herself with Ironclad.... \! Let's use
Vita effectively against strong opponents!

I think it's a good idea to start with debuffing at first.
\! Unlike other characters, she's not really a character who
relies on secret techniques for now. \. But that's also
strong.

Should we debuff 'physical' or 'magic' abilities...? \!
Let's try to judge based on the enemy's appearance!

Ah, she also has a characteristic normal attack. \! With the
Giant Sword, it triggers follow-up attacks from allies. \!
With the Iron Ball, it performs a 3-hit attack. \! The Bow
has an area-of-effect range.

When you use the Secret Technique, it becomes an Ultimate
and you can add all elements to your Normal Attacks! \! When
the flow is stable, let's give it a shot!!

First of all, she's fast! She can quickly heal and support
other characters... and more! \! Since she moves first, you
can rely on her!

While dealing abundant AoE damage to weak enemies, if you're
lucky, you can also immobilize them with status ailments! \!
A reliable ally for a comfortable journey!! \! The
performance is also a delight for loop gamers!

In tough battles, she's incredibly strong as a supporter! \.
With her special move's firepower buff, she can greatly
enhance her allies! \! Let's use it in sync with other
characters' special moves! \! It's a performance that will
make gacha gamers smile too!

I think her usage is where her skills shine...! Let's start
by casually using her special move!

events.name: ◇開始イベント　バックアップ

parameters:
Thank you for playing the Demo Version! Well... this is the
kind of story it is. Some people might have been confused
because it's quite different from Teekyuu in terms of
atmosphere...
As for the development after this...

First, the story of Vega will begin. And there will be a
sinister conspiracy... How will Laura and the others' fate
unfold...? I put a lot of effort into this one too. Maybe a
bit too much.

In the demo version of Vega, there weren't many scenes where
she could shine, and that's a little regrettable... There
are plenty of moments where she can make a big impact
though... People who like Nasuno- senpai will probably like
her.

And... I couldn't show you Tita who became a love beast, and
it's painful...

This girl, you know. She fell in love at first sight with
Lunaroa and will become a troublesome girl who interrupts
their yuri relationship! What will happen to Laura's
love...!?

Ah! What on earth will happen...!! ...Well, let's not drag
it out. Since you're here, why don't you take a look...
Teehee!!

Alright! If you're interested, why don't you come talk to
me?
And I briefly mentioned... Lunaroa's school life and such...
And as for Laura... No, let's not say that.

...Well, there are other things too, but that's the general
idea!

Before that... umm. It's going to be a bit of a self-
indulgence but... if you could spare me a little time...

One day, I suddenly felt like it... Maybe I should try
making a game and really focus on it for once in my life!
...Well, I started making this with a light-hearted feeling.

...Well, I understand the feeling. If you're a fan of games,
I think you've probably considered it at least once, and
there are plenty of famous masterpieces out there. Whether
or not you actually make one is a different story though.

...The problem is the enormous amount of working time it
takes. If you work on it in between other things, it can
take 4 to 5 years. Most people are unable to complete it.
And when it fails, it's called an Eternal.

To prevent that... in order to block the escape route, the
creator threw away their job. In other words, they kept
making it without earning any money. And then it took about
2000 hours or so...
Hehe, it's not just about focusing, you know.

Well, how should I put it... Even if you sell it for a fee,
I wonder if you can actually recover the costs... Honestly,
it's extremely difficult. Even if you calculate it based on
the minimum hourly wage... You know, right?
And, well... umm. I know it's embarrassing, but...

\{To kind-hearted people who love this kind of thing...!!
\!I was hoping you could help me by buying the full version!
Would you be willing to do that!?

Well... I understand it myself. \!I'm talking about
something dirty...\. You must be thinking that, right? It's
only natural to enjoy entertainment for free, so talking
about money is absurd...

But even big companies are doing crowdfunding these days!
Individuals are even more desperate, aren't they...!!!

Ah, that's right! I think you can understand the story since
you've seen the main part, but maybe the feeling of battles
isn't explained enough. So, umm... that's what I wanted to
say.

It's good to fight against these Unique Monsters!! \!I think
you'll get a sense of the flow of battle! \.Don't hold back,
go all out and give it your all!!

If you're not good at battles, I'll teach you! \!...But if
you don't want to fight, you can ignore me!

That's all! Thank you for listening!! \!We look forward to
your next visit!!

Ah, are you leaving? If so, there's one favor I'd like to
ask...

When you go back from there, you'll return to the Title
Screen. If... if it's okay with you, could you...

Could you leave a nice comment on the title screen when you
go back?

No, I understand. You're thinking something like Begging for
likes, right...?

But, I still want it...! A scenery where the title screen is
filled with comments like It was fun! or something...!!

By the way, I'd be happy if you could also give some
feedback. It would be really helpful because it increases
the capacity for posting...! I want to secure the capacity
and return to being a regular member.

I'd be happy if you could follow me on Twitter too! Even
though I don't update it at all...!

Fan art is also very welcome...! If I find it, I'll retweet
it without question!!

I would be happy if I could receive gifts too! Honestly, I
don't really understand it well though!

...Ah, sorry for keeping you. Are you finally leaving this
time?
Ah, are you finally going home this time?!
There's a strong-looking monster.... Will you fight it?

It's a monument for defeating unique monsters.... \! Lovey-
dovey Couple, would you like to have a rematch? \!

Oh no, you defeated me...? I was supposed to put up more of
a fight...

...Fine, I have no choice! If that's the case, I'll become
an additional boss!! Come at me!!

Heheh! There's no way you can win against me...! Come on,
bring it on!!

That person is Mr./Ms. 〇〇. Even though they had a job offer,
they decided to pursue a career in gaming and turned down
the job offer. They are a strong-willed individual. Oh my...
They are the one who created the second boss.

What the young person needs is not sympathy, but
encouragement. I hope you can give them some words of
support for the future. And now, please leave a comment...!!
\SE[4]W-Would you like to hear my story...?

That person is Ms. AGNES. She's a modern person who just
quit a black company! She helped out with various things in
place of the completely clueless author of Programming!

I want everyone to give warm words of encouragement to him,
who is being tossed around by the rough waves of modern
society. Come on, give him some clever comments...!!

\SE[3]How about changing the music for a change of mood?
\SE[0]Do you have any favorites, I wonder?

\SE[14]Haa...!? \SE[41]Ahem... Well, I guess there's no
helping it...!!
Um, did you defeat it...? That was my trump card...?

Huh? So you have some combat sense after all...? D-Don't get
the wrong idea, just a little bit! I still haven't fully
acknowledged you yet!!

Even if you look at me like that, I don't have any more
trump cards! If you're jealous, then go buy the full
version...!

I was thinking about a plan to have players participate in
the game as NPCs if they have any requests... like,
something along those lines.

I couldn't come up with an efficient way to communicate with
a large number of people, so I gave up. If there's any good
method, it would be great...

Nice to meet everyone. I'm AGNES, mainly in charge of the
system. Thank you very much for playing Zero Moon Laura!
Since this is my first time creating a game, there may be
some areas that are not perfect, but I hope you enjoy it
until the end!

That person is Mr./Ms. 〇〇. They are a modern person who just
quit a black company! They helped out with various things in
place of the completely clueless author, like programming!

I want everyone to give warm words of encouragement to him,
who has been tossed around by the rough waves of modern
society. Come on, give him a clever comment...!!
